    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "This addon adds a context menu entry to the address book that creates a TeX file containing a letter template that is directed at the contacts selected. It afterwards opens your favorite TeX editor to write your letter's content. You can provide your own templates to always use the same style or sender information for your letters. An example for such a template is included."
    },
    "developer_comments": {
        "en-US": "This is the first release of this addon, and I am sure there are some bugs in it, but I would be grateful if you gave me some feedback about its functionality. For the next versions, providing other formats than TeX and supporting gender-specific salutations."
    },
